title: MisterMusic Show 361 indie,alternative,rock radio
description:
MisterMusic Show 361 - [2 hours] 192 kbps MP3 stereo-


On the show this week, it's a two hour mish-mash of indie, alternative and classic hits from over 5 decades of rock.
The 'Oldie of the Week' was a huge hit in July 1982. It spent 3 weeks at number one, and was the group's most commercially successful song to date.

The MisterMusic Show is broadcast weekly and heard globally on RockXS internet radio.
